    <img src="project3.jpg" alt="Art Project 3">
    <div class="caption">Caption for Art Project 3</div>
    <div class="description">Artwork number 3, is the drawing where we can see a girl with two masks, the first mask looks scared and the other mean and crazy. The figures and faces look exaggerated, containing no other color than black which makes it look like a rough sketch, and also the red signature that author had left. What makes this picture differ from others is the style and colors or to be more specific it’s lack. What makes this artwork even more special is the fact that first it was an actual sketch made by pencil, that I had put into the program and began to draw over it.  
</div>
